      <title>特朗普威胁后，魁北克表示对液化天然气和石油项目持开放态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/quebec-says-it-s-open-to-lng-oil-projects-after-trump-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[魁北克长期以来一直拒绝在其领土上修建新的石油和天然气管道的提议。美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对加拿大的威胁可能会改变这一现状。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/quebec-says-it-s-open-to-lng-oil-projects-after-trump-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 18:34:25 GMT</pubDate>
